  "html": "\u003cdiv id=\"readability-page-1\" class=\"page\"\u003e\u003carticle\u003e\u003cp data-component=\"headline-block\"\u003e\u003ch2\u003eWhy the skies turned red over the UK this weekend\u003c/h2\u003e\u003c/p\u003e\u003cfigure\u003e\u003cdiv data-component=\"image-block\"\u003e\u003cp\u003e\u003cimg src=\"https://www.bbc.com/bbcx/grey-placeholder.png\"/\u003e\u003cimg sizes=\"(min-width: 1280px) 50vw, (min-width: 1008px) 66vw, 96vw\" srcset=\"https://ichef.bbci.co.uk/news/240/cpsprodpb/8197/live/8f6997e0-5d9f-11ef-b75d-6329e6f25195.jpg.webp 240w,https://ichef.bbci.co.uk/news/320/cpsprodpb/8197/live/8f6997e0-5d9f-11ef-b75d-6329e6f25195.jpg.webp 320w,https://ichef.bbci.co.uk/news/480/cpsprodpb/8197/live/8f6997e0-5d9f-11ef-b75d-6329e6f25195.jpg.webp 480w,https://ichef.bbci.co.uk/news/640/cpsprodpb/8197/live/8f6997e0-5d9f-11ef-b75d-6329e6f25195.jpg.webp 640w,https://ichef.bbci.co.uk/news/800/cpsprodpb/8197/live/8f6997e0-5d9f-11ef-b75d-6329e6f25195.jpg.webp 800w,https://ichef.bbci.co.uk/news/1024/cpsprodpb/8197/live/8f6997e0-5d9f-11ef-b75d-6329e6f25195.jpg.webp 1024w,https://ichef.bbci.co.uk/news/1536/cpsprodpb/8197/live/8f6997e0-5d9f-11ef-b75d-6329e6f25195.jpg.webp 1536w\" src=\"https://ichef.bbci.co.uk/news/480/cpsprodpb/8197/live/8f6997e0-5d9f-11ef-b75d-6329e6f25195.jpg.webp\" loading=\"eager\" alt=\"Peter Barrett / BBC Weather Watchers This morning\u0026#39;s sunrise in Hornchurch, East London\"/\u003e\u003cspan\u003ePeter Barrett / BBC Weather Watchers\u003c/span\u003e\u003c/p\u003e\u003c/div\u003e\u003cp data-component=\"caption-block\"\u003e\u003cfigcaption\u003eSunday\u0026#39;s sunrise in Hornchurch, East London\u003c/figcaption\u003e\u003c/p\u003e\u003c/figure\u003e\u003cdiv data-component=\"text-block\"\u003e\u003cp\u003eSmoke from wildfires across the Atlantic has brought spectacular vivid colours to sunsets and sunrises across the UK this weekend.\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003eFires have blazed across North America this summer, and smoke particles have been carried by the jet stream to the skies above the British Isles.\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003eThe unusual hues should continue until Monday, when more unsettled weather will begin to disperse the smoke in the upper atmosphere.\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003eBut skywatchers could also be in for a treat on Monday night, when a rare blue supermoon appears above the UK.\u003c/p\u003e\u003c/div\u003e\u003cfigure\u003e\u003cdiv data-component=\"image-block\"\u003e\u003cp\u003e\u003cimg src=\"https://www.bbc.com/bbcx/grey-placeholder.png\"/\u003e\u003cimg sizes=\"(min-width: 1280px) 50vw, (min-width: 1008px) 66vw, 96vw\" srcset=\"https://ichef.bbci.co.uk/news/240/cpsprodpb/a6f2/live/c9ee1310-5da3-11ef-9a47-17b2433a2105.png.webp 240w,https://ichef.bbci.co.uk/news/320/cpsprodpb/a6f2/live/c9ee1310-5da3-11ef-9a47-17b2433a2105.png.webp 320w,https://ichef.bbci.co.uk/news/480/cpsprodpb/a6f2/live/c9ee1310-5da3-11ef-9a47-17b2433a2105.png.webp 480w,https://ichef.bbci.co.uk/news/640/cpsprodpb/a6f2/live/c9ee1310-5da3-11ef-9a47-17b2433a2105.png.webp 640w,https://ichef.bbci.co.uk/news/800/cpsprodpb/a6f2/live/c9ee1310-5da3-11ef-9a47-17b2433a2105.png.webp 800w,https://ichef.bbci.co.uk/news/1024/cpsprodpb/a6f2/live/c9ee1310-5da3-11ef-9a47-17b2433a2105.png.webp 1024w,https://ichef.bbci.co.uk/news/1536/cpsprodpb/a6f2/live/c9ee1310-5da3-11ef-9a47-17b2433a2105.png.webp 1536w\" src=\"https://ichef.bbci.co.uk/news/480/cpsprodpb/a6f2/live/c9ee1310-5da3-11ef-9a47-17b2433a2105.png.webp\" loading=\"lazy\" alt=\"John Bradburn/ BBC Weather Watchers Red sunset in Buxton, Derbyshire\"/\u003e\u003cspan\u003eJohn Bradburn/ BBC Weather Watchers\u003c/span\u003e\u003c/p\u003e\u003c/div\u003e\u003cp data-component=\"caption-block\"\u003e\u003cfigcaption\u003eSunset on Sunday in Buxton, Derbyshire, had a very red tinge\u003c/figcaption\u003e\u003c/p\u003e\u003c/figure\u003e\u003cfigure\u003e\u003cdiv data-component=\"image-block\"\u003e\u003cp\u003e\u003cimg src=\"https://www.bbc.com/bbcx/grey-placeholder.png\"