ws/240/cpsprodpb/d3ca/live/1178f030-5d75-11ef-8c32-f3c2bc7494c6.jpg.webp 240w,https://ichef.bbci.co.uk/news/320/cpsprodpb/d3ca/live/1178f030-5d75-11ef-8c32-f3c2bc7494c6.jpg.webp 320w,https://ichef.bbci.co.uk/news/480/cpsprodpb/d3ca/live/1178f030-5d75-11ef-8c32-f3c2bc7494c6.jpg.webp 480w,https://ichef.bbci.co.uk/news/640/cpsprodpb/d3ca/live/1178f030-5d75-11ef-8c32-f3c2bc7494c6.jpg.webp 640w,https://ichef.bbci.co.uk/news/800/cpsprodpb/d3ca/live/1178f030-5d75-11ef-8c32-f3c2bc7494c6.jpg.webp 800w,https://ichef.bbci.co.uk/news/1024/cpsprodpb/d3ca/live/1178f030-5d75-11ef-8c32-f3c2bc7494c6.jpg.webp 1024w,https://ichef.bbci.co.uk/news/1536/cpsprodpb/d3ca/live/1178f030-5d75-11ef-8c32-f3c2bc7494c6.jpg.webp 1536w\" src=\"https://ichef.bbci.co.uk/news/480/cpsprodpb/d3ca/live/1178f030-5d75-11ef-8c32-f3c2bc7494c6.jpg.webp\" loading=\"lazy\" alt=\"Copernicus Infrared image showing smoke travelling from North America across the Atlantic to the UK\"/\u003e\u003cspan\u003eCopernicus\u003c/span\u003e\u003c/p\u003e\u003c/div\u003e\u003cp data-component=\"caption-block\"\u003e\u003cfigcaption\u003eThis image forecasts what the smoke from North America travelling over the Atlantic to the UK will look like on Monday 18:00 BST\u003c/figcaption\u003e\u003c/p\u003e\u003c/figure\u003e\u003cp data-component=\"subheadline-block\"\u003e\u003ch2\u003eWhat is a supermoon?\u003c/h2\u003e\u003c/p\u003e\u003cdiv data-component=\"text-block\"\u003e\u003cp\u003eThe UK skies will play host to a rare lunar phenomenon on Monday night - a blue super moon.\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003eMonday\u0026#39;s full moon is not just a supermoon. It is also a blue moon but those hoping to see a bluish shade to the satellite are out of luck.\u003c/p\u003e\u003c/div\u003e\u003cfigure\u003e\u003cdiv data-component=\"image-block\"\u003e\u003cp\u003e\u003cimg src=\"https://www.bbc.com/bbcx/grey-placeholder.png\"/\u003e\u003cimg sizes=\"(min-width: 1280px) 50vw, (min-width: 1008px) 66vw, 96vw\" srcset=\"https://ichef.bbci.co.uk/news/240/cpsprodpb/9104/live/13ecc140-5d73-11ef-8c32-f3c2bc7494c6.jpg.webp 240w,https://ichef.bbci.co.uk/news/320/cpsprodpb/9104/live/13ecc140-5d73-11ef-8c32-f3c2bc7494c6.jpg.webp 320w,https://ichef.bbci.co.uk/news/480/cpsprodpb/9104/live/13ecc140-5d73-11ef-8c32-f3c2bc7494c6.jpg.webp 480w,https://ichef.bbci.co.uk/news/640/cpsprodpb/9104/live/13ecc140-5d73-11ef-8c32-f3c2bc7494c6.jpg.webp 640w,https://ichef.bbci.co.uk/news/800/cpsprodpb/9104/live/13ecc140-5d73-11ef-8c32-f3c2bc7494c6.jpg.webp 800w,https://ichef.bbci.co.uk/news/1024/cpsprodpb/9104/live/13ecc140-5d73-11ef-8c32-f3c2bc7494c6.jpg.webp 1024w,https://ichef.bbci.co.uk/news/1536/cpsprodpb/9104/live/13ecc140-5d73-11ef-8c32-f3c2bc7494c6.jpg.webp 1536w\" src=\"https://ichef.bbci.co.uk/news/480/cpsprodpb/9104/live/13ecc140-5d73-11ef-8c32-f3c2bc7494c6.jpg.webp\" loading=\"lazy\" alt=\"PA A super blue moon, which looks bright orange, next to the Balmoral Clock in Edinburgh last August\"/\u003e\u003cspan\u003ePA\u003c/span\u003e\u003c/p\u003e\u003c/div\u003e\u003cp data-component=\"caption-block\"\u003e\u003cfigcaption\u003eA super blue moon, seen here next to the Balmoral Clock in Edinburgh, last August\u003c/figcaption\u003e\u003c/p\u003e\u003c/figure\u003e\u003cdiv data-component=\"text-block\"\u003e\u003cp\u003eA blue moon refers to the third full moon in a season with four full moons, as is the case with this full moon. It can also refer to the second full moon in a month with two full moons.\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003eA supermoon appears brighter and bigger than usual because the Moon\u0026#39;s orbit brings it closer to earth.\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003eThe last time the UK witnessed a \u003ca target=\"_self\" href=\"https://www.bbc.co.uk/news/science-environment-66657541\"\u003ecombined super blue moon was last August\u003c/a\u003e - but if you miss it, the next one is reportedly not due until 2037.  \u003c/p\u003e\u003c/div\u003e\u003cfigure\u003e\u003cdiv data-component=\"image-block\"\u003e\u003cp\u003e\u003cimg src=\"https://www.bbc.com/bbcx/grey-placeholder.png\"/\u003e\u003cimg sizes=\"(min-width: 1280px) 50vw, (min-width: 1008px) 66vw, 96vw\" srcset=\"https://ichef.bbci.co.uk/news/240/cpsprodpb/961d/live/07c237d0-5d8f-11ef-be42-01d782fcb8e3.jpg.webp 240w,https://ichef.bbci.co.uk/news/320/cpsprodpb/961d/live/07c237d0-5d8f-11ef-be42-01d782fcb8e3.jpg.webp 320w,https://ichef.bbci.co.uk/news/480/cpsprodpb/961d/live/07c237d0-5d8f-11ef-be42-01d782fcb8e3.jpg.webp 480w,https://ichef.bbci.co.uk/news/640/cpsprodpb/961d/live/07c237d0-5d8f-11ef-be42-01d782fcb8e3.jpg.webp 640w,https://ichef.bbci.co.uk/news/800/cpsprodpb/961d/live/07c237d0-5d8f-11ef-be42-01d782fcb8e3.jpg.webp 800w,https://ichef.bbci.co.uk/news/1024/cpsprodpb/961d/live/07c237d0-5d8f-11ef-be42-01d782fcb8e3.jpg.webp 1024w,https://ichef.bbci.co.uk/news/1536/cpsprodpb/961d/live/07c237d0-5d8f-11ef-be42-01d782fcb8e3.jpg.webp 1536w\" src=\"https://ichef.bbci.co.uk/news/480/cpsprodpb/961d/live/07c237d0-5d8f-11ef-be42-01d782fcb8e3.jpg.webp\" loading=\"lazy\" alt=\"Diana / BBC Weather Watchers  Sunset in Dunstable, Central Bedfordshire, with purplish skies and a butterfly kite flying past the sun\u0026#39;s silhouette\"/\u003e\u003cspan\u003eDiana / BBC Weather Watchers \u003c/span\u003e\u003c/p\u003e\u003c/div\u003e\u003cp data-component=\"caption-block\"\u003e\u003cfigcaption\u003eLast night\u0026#39;s sunset in Dunstable, Central Bedfordshire\u003c/figcaption\u003e\u003c/p\u003e\u003c/figure\u003e\u003c/article\u003e\u003c/div\u003e",
